Package it.unipr.sowide.actosis.util.space

Class IntPairVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipr.sowide.actosis.util.space.IntPairVector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IntPair, IntVectorAPI<IntPair>, VectorAPI<java.lang.Integer,​IntPair>, java.io.Serializable
    public class IntPairVector
extends java.lang.Object
implements IntPair, IntVectorAPI<IntPair>
    The IntPairVector( class represents an immutable vector in a 2D discrete space. It provides some methods that manipulate its coordinates values, but their return value is always represented by a new immutable vector.
    See Also:
